Package com.googlecode.aluminumproject.libraries.text.actions

Class Summary
Mute Mutes or unmutes the output of the action that it contributes to by replacing its writer with a toggleable writer.
NewlinesToPreserve Preserves a number of connecting newlines of the body text of the action that it contributes to.
SpacesToPreserve Preserves a number of contiguous spaces of the body text of the action that it contributes to.
TabsToPreserve Preserves a number of adjacent tabs of the body text of the action that it contributes to.
Trim Trims the body text of the action it contributes to.
TrimLines Trims each line of the body text of the action that it contributes to.
WhitespaceToPreserve Abstract superclass of action contributions that replace the current writer with a preserve whitespace writer.
